---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import footerBg from '../assets/images/footer-bg.jpg';
---
<footer id="contact" class="relative pt-24 pb-8 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <Image src={footerBg} alt="Background" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#2b221b]/85 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            
            <div class="fade-up">
                <h2 class="text-6xl font-serif text-[#E5D4C3] mb-8 tracking-wide">Контакты</h2>
                
                <div class="space-y-8 font-light tracking-wide text-lg text-white/80">
                    <div>
                        <p>Чебоксары, Чувашская Республика</p>
                        <p class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                            <span>ул. Социалистическая 2г</span>
                            <a href="https://yandex.ru/maps/?text=56.108023,47.177126" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider border border-gold/40 hover:border-gold hover:bg-gold hover:text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300">
                                <i data-feather="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-gold-light"></i>
                                <span>На карте</span>
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-1">
                        <p>Телефон: <a href="tel:+79373864064" class="hover:text-gold transition">+7 (937) 386-40-64</a></p>
                        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:nevestaagntsa@gmail.com" class="hover:text-gold transition">nevestaagntsa@gmail.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 text-[#A67B5B]">Соцсети</h3>
                        <div class="flex gap-4">
                            <a href="https://rutube.ru/channel/42730775/" target="_blank" aria-label="Rutube" class="hover:text-gold transition transform hover:scale-110">
                                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon></svg>
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://t.me/nevestaagntsa" target="_blank" aria-label="Telegram" class="hover:text-gold transition transform hover:scale-110">
                                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon></svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="fade-up md:pl-10 md:border-l border-white/10">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#A67B5B] uppercase tracking-widest">Время служений</h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 text-white/90 text-lg font-light">
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-2">
                        <span>Воскресенье</span>
                        <span>10:00</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-2">
                        <span>Вторник (Домашние группы)</span>
                        <span>18:00</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-2">
                        <span>Четверг (Альфа курс)</span>
                        <span>18:00</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-2">
                        <div>
                            <span>Пятница</span>
                            <span class="block text-sm text-white/40">(Изучение Библии / Молитва)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-right">
                            <span>17:30</span>
                            <span class="block text-sm text-white/40">19:00</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 text-sm text-white/50 italic">
                        *Возможны изменения в праздничные дни
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
            &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} МРОХВЕП<br>"Церковь "Невеста Агнца"
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
